ygData.messageBody:
omg! you just made me remember that i was once a bard in the world of
norrath! but that is long ago, i quit around mid 2002 (57, one blue to 58).
well, i still meet some of my eq friends, i got to know a lot of people
through eq, rl friends now. its always funny to think back and remember the
old days and all the stuff you went through together.

cheers to all
tobi
